comment: Gee (NOP) sets the screen on Noah (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Noah (CHI) makes contact with Davis (NOP) on his shot attempt.
Evans (NOP) actively guards an opponent while in the lane.
Davis (NOP) makes contact with Rose's (CHI) arm and affects his pass.
Cunningham (NOP) slides into Rose (CHI) and affects his RSBQ.
Brooks (CHI) does not step out of bounds on the sideline.
Gordon (NOP) and Gasol (CHI) engage briefly in the lane.
Gasol's (CHI) shot does not hit the rim, resulting in a 24-second violation.
Noah (CHI) affects Davis' (NOP) FOM off ball in the lane.
Noah (CHI) is in legal guarding position on the post curl play by Davis (NOP).
Davis (NOP) is actively guarding Gasol (CHI) and therefore may be in the lane for more than three seconds.
Evans (NOP) is not actively guarding in the lane for more than three seconds.
